      • beginScope

        public void beginScope()
        to begin a new scope, such as entering a class definition, function, compound statement

      • define

        public void define(Name key,
                   Symbol value)
            throws Redefine
        To define a name in current scope
        参数:
        key - the corresponding Name object
        value - the corresponding cn.ficos.Compiler.Gadgets.Symbol object that contains corresponding information
        抛出:
        Redefine - throw if the key has been defined in current scope

      • endScope

        public void endScope()
        to end a scope, recover previous scope

        public Type lookUpType(java.lang.String typeName)
                throws Undefined
        A shortcut for type looking up
        参数:
        typeName - the name of type to look up
        返回:
        the required type
        抛出:
        Undefined - the "undefine" error

      • resolve

        public Symbol resolve(Name key)
               throws Undefined
        To find a Name's corresponding information, which is stored as cn.ficos.Compiler.Gadgets.Symbol
        参数:
        key - the Name to be looked up
        返回:
        the corresponding cn.ficos.Compiler.Gadgets.Symbol
        抛出:
        Undefined - throw if the key has not been defined in current or formal scopes
